compound_physical_parameters.safety_comments: Use the normal handling procedures for an olefinic ester. The Ames mutagenic screening test indicated no detectable mutagenic activity. The acute oral toxicity (LD50) value in mice was 4.0 g/kg.

storage_recommendations.special_storage: dark brown bottle; stored under inert atmosphere in refrigerator.

compound_sensitive_to.other: The material is relatively unstable to heat, light and oxygen (air) and will decompose within 1 month at room temperature. More rapid decomposition will occur at higher temperatures.
